text: WKRA-FM (92.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Holly Springs, Mississippi. The station is owned by Billy R. Autry, and airs a gospel music format. The station was assigned the WKRA-FM call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on December 2, 1974. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for WKRA-FM * FCC History Card for WKRA-FM * KRA-FM Category:Radio stations established in 1977 Category:1977 establishments in Mississippi Category:Gospel radio stations in the United States Category:Marshall County, Mississippi KRA-FM
